{"tha-ap136:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap136:0.2":"Sobhitavagga ","tha-ap136:0.3":"4 Pupphacchadaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap136:1.1":"“Sunando nama namena, ","tha-ap136:1.2":"brahmano mantaparagu; ","tha-ap136:1.3":"Ajjhayako yacayogo, ","tha-ap136:1.4":"vajapeyyam ayajayi. ","tha-ap136:2.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap136:2.2":"aggo karuniko isi; ","tha-ap136:2.3":"Janatam anukampanto, ","tha-ap136:2.4":"ambare cankami tada. ","tha-ap136:3.1":"Cankamitvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap136:3.2":"sabbannu lokanayako; ","tha-ap136:3.3":"Mettaya aphari satte, ","tha-ap136:3.4":"appamane nirupadhi. ","tha-ap136:4.1":"Vante chetvana pupphani, ","tha-ap136:4.2":"brahmano mantaparagu; ","tha-ap136:4.3":"Sabbe sisse samanetva, ","tha-ap136:4.4":"akase ukkhipapayi. ","tha-ap136:5.1":"Yavata nagaram asi, ","tha-ap136:5.2":"pupphanam chadanam tada; ","tha-ap136:5.3":"Buddhassa anubhavena, ","tha-ap136:5.4":"sattaham na vigacchatha. ","tha-ap136:6.1":"Teneva sukkamulena, ","tha-ap136:6.2":"anubhotvana sampada; ","tha-ap136:6.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap136:6.4":"tinno loke visattikam. ","tha-ap136:7.1":"Ekarase kappasate, ","tha-ap136:7.2":"pancatimsasu khattiya; ","tha-ap136:7.3":"Ambaramsasanama te, ","tha-ap136:7.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap136:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap136:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap136:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap136:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pupphacchadaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap136:10.1":"Pupphacchadaniyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}